principled since White has the bishop pair. It leads to an interesting game:} (
{Black is fine in case of} 13. Qxc4 Nbxd5 14. Rd1 c6 15. e4 Qg4 $1 $11 16. h3
Nb6 17. Rxd8+ Bxd8 18. Qxc6+ bxc6 19. hxg4 Nxg4 20. f3 Nf6 21. Be3 $44) 13...
